    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It's in really nice shape and has been well-loved, running smoothly and ready to hit the road with its new owner! It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
