    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The drivetrain features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery. Suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein B16 coilovers and Turner Motorsport bushings, sharpening the turn-in and maintaining the car's neutral handling bias. While the aesthetic reflects a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical vitals are optimized for performance and longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Well-maintained vehicle. Clean interior. Mechanically sound. Minor exterior wear. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
