      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced dual-VANOS system for optimal cam phasing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under high torque loads. The suspension retains its tactile feedback with refreshed bushings and original dampers, providing excellent turn-in and lateral stability. A driver-focused machine with a clean mechanical pedigree.",
